'''飓风温贝托'''（{{lang-en|Hurricane Humberto}}）是[[2007年大西洋飓风季|2007年大西洋飓风季]]形成的第八场获得命名的风暴和第三场飓风，虽然规模很小，但在[[登陆_(气象学)|登陆]]前的增强速度却比有纪录以来任何一场[[大西洋飓风季|大西洋飓风]]都要快。系统于2007年9月12日在[[墨西哥湾|墨西哥湾]]西北部发展成型，成为[[热带气旋|热带气旋]]后[[快速增强|快速增强]]，于9月13日以风速每小时150公里强度吹袭[[德克萨斯州|德克萨斯州]][[高岛_(德克萨斯州)|高岛]]。上岸后风暴稳步减弱，最终于9月14日在[[乔治亚州|乔治亚州]]西北部上空同逐渐逼近的[[冷锋|冷锋]]相互影响而逐渐消散。

温贝托造成的破坏程度不高，估计损失数额约为5000万美元。风暴产生的最大降雨量为358.9毫米，测得的最强阵风时速为137公里。暴雨引发大面积洪灾，导致数十户民居受损或被毁，多条公路被迫封闭。部分树木倒塌，输电线缆中断，数十万用户失去供电。飓风在德克萨斯州夺走一条人命，气旋逐渐深入内陆期间，[[美国东南部|美国东南部]]普遍出现降水。

== 气象历史 ==
{{storm path|Humberto 2007 track.png}}
飓风温贝托源自9月5日离开[[佛罗里达州|佛罗里达州]]南岸的[[锋_(气象)|锋面]][[低压槽|槽]]残留，[[2007年热带风暴加布里埃尔|热带风暴加布里埃尔]]也是由这股残留催生<ref>{{cite report | date = 2008-04-28 | title = WMO RA IV Hurricane Committee Final Report | accessdate = 2016-07-28 | publisher = World Meteorological Organization | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303165149/http://www.wmo.int/pages/prog/www/tcp/documents/FINALREPORT_HC-30_EN_withoutTechPlan.pdf | archivedate = 2016-03-03 | format = [[便携式文档格式|PDF]] | url = http://www.wmo.int/pages/prog/www/tcp/documents/FINALREPORT_HC-30_EN_withoutTechPlan.pdf }}</ref><ref name="humbertotcr">{{cite report | author = Eric S. Blake | date = 2007-11-28 | title = Hurricane Humberto Tropical Cyclone Report | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2016-07-28 | archivedate = 2015-10-02 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151002011430/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/data/tcr/AL092007_Humberto.pdf | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/data/tcr/AL092007_Humberto.pdf }}</ref>。微弱的地面槽同[[地球大气层|上层]][[低气压|低气压]]天气系统共同作用，令[[古巴|古巴]]西部到[[墨西哥湾|墨西哥湾]]东部海域出现分布混乱的阵雨和雷阵雨<ref>{{cite report | author = Jack Beven | date = 2007-09-08 | title = Tropical Weather Outlook | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160728031425/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/text/TWOAT/2007/TWOAT.200709082118.txt | publisher = National Hurricane Center | archivedate = 2016-07-28 | deadurl = no | format = [[文本文件|TXT]] | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/text/TWOAT/2007/TWOAT.200709082118.txt | access-date = 2016-07-28 }}</ref>。系统朝[[罗盘方位|西北偏西]]方向缓慢前进，起初因受[[风切变|风切变]]的不利影响而无法发展<ref>{{cite report | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160728031920/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/text/TWOAT/2007/TWOAT.200709100914.txt | author = Jamie Rhome | date = 2007-09-10 | title = Tropical Weather Outlook | publisher = National Hurricane Center | format = TXT | accessdate = 2016-07-28 | archivedate = 2016-07-28 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/text/TWOAT/2007/TWOAT.200709100914.txt | deadurl = no }}</ref>。到了9月11日晚，外界环境已有改善<ref>{{cite report | author1 = Richard Pasch | author2 = Chris Landsea | date = 2007-09-11 | title = Tropical Weather Outlook | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2016-07-28 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160728034329/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/text/TWOAT/2007/TWOAT.200709120201.txt | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2016-07-28 | format = TXT | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/text/TWOAT/2007/TWOAT.200709120201.txt }}</ref>，扰动天气上空的[[对流|对流]]到次日早上已有显著增长<ref name="912two">{{cite report | author = Michelle Mainelli | date = 2007-09-12 | title = Tropical Weather Outlook | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160728034505/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/text/TWOAT/2007/TWOAT.200709120920.txt | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/text/TWOAT/2007/TWOAT.200709120920.txt | accessdate = 2016-07-28 | publisher = National Hurricane Center | archivedate = 2016-07-28 | deadurl = no | format = TXT }}</ref>。系统沿中层[[高压脊|高压脊]]的西部边缘移动，在此期间转朝西北方向缓慢飘移并快速组织。雷达图像显示其中有松散的[[雨带|带状特征]]形成，浮标所测数据表明已有地面环流存在，[[国家飓风中心|美国国家飓风中心]]为此将位于[[德克萨斯州|德克萨斯州]][[马塔哥达县|马塔哥达县]]小镇[[马塔哥达_(德克萨斯州)|马塔哥达]]（{{lang|en|Matagorda}}）东南方向约100公里洋面的天气系统归类成[[2007年大西洋飓风季|本季]]第九号热带低气压。<ref name="disc1">{{cite report | author = James Franklin | date = 2007-09-12 | title = Tropical Depression Nine Discussion One | publisher = National Hurricane Center | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304223301/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2007/al09/al092007.discus.001.shtml | deadurl = no | accessdate = 2016-07-28 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2007/al09/al092007.discus.001.shtml? | archivedate = 2016-03-04 }}</ref>

气象机构起初认为，这片天气系统成为热带气旋后会缓慢增强，达到[[最大持续风速|风力时速]]75公里的最高强度<ref name="disc1" />。成型不到三小时后，热带低气压就增强成热带风暴并获名“温贝托”（{{lang|en|Humberto}}）<ref>{{cite report | author = James Franklin | date = 2007-09-12 | title = Tropical Storm Humberto Public Advisory One-A | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160701070203/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2007/al09/al092007.public_a.001.shtml | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2007/al09/al092007.public_a.001.shtml | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2016-07-28 | archivedate = 2016-07-01 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。风暴的规模偏小，在转向东北偏北同时继续快速组织，到9月13日清晨，雷达图像表明其中已有[[风眼|风眼]]形成<ref name="disc3">{{cite report | author = Richard Pasch | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160701071026/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2007/al09/al092007.discus.003.shtml | date = 2007-09-12 | title = Tropical Storm Humberto Discussion Three | publisher = National Hurricane Center | deadurl = no | accessdate = 2016-07-28 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2007/al09/al092007.discus.003.shtml? | archivedate = 2016-07-01 }}</ref>。根据[[飓风猎人|飓风猎人]]所测数据，气象部门于[[协调世界时|协调世界时]]9月13日早上5点15分把位于德克萨斯州近海仅20公里洋面的温贝托升级成飓风<ref name="disc4">{{cite report | author1 = Michelle Mainellimcinerney | author2 = Lixion Avila | date = 2007-09-13 | title = Hurricane Humberto Special Discussion Four | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2016-07-28 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2007/al09/al092007.discus.004.shtml? | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304102410/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2007/al09/al092007.discus.004.shtml | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2016-03-04 }}</ref>。{{lang|en|[[协调世界时|UTC]]}}早上7点左右，气旋从德克萨斯州高岛（{{lang|en|High Island}}）东侧数英里处[[登陆_(气象学)|登陆]]。飓风的风眼层次分明，周围由强劲对流层层环绕，飓风猎人在风暴登陆两小时后仍然测得每小时140公里的持续风速，<ref name="disc5">{{cite report | author1 = Michelle Mainellimcinerney | author2 = Lixion Avila | date = 2007-09-13 | title = Hurricane Humberto Discussion Five | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2016-07-28 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160701071508/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2007/al09/al092007.discus.005.shtml | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2007/al09/al092007.discus.005.shtml? | archivedate = 2016-07-01 | deadurl = no }}</ref>但经风暴过后的重新分析，美国国家飓风中心认定气旋此时的风速更高，约达每小时150公里<ref name="humbertotcr" />。

美国国家飓风中心在当时的实际操作中估计，温贝托的风速提升幅度达每小时85公里，是有纪录以来在登陆前夕增强速度最快的热带气旋。风暴继续朝东北前进并保持在一级飓风强度，风眼先后经过[[杰佛逊县_(得克萨斯州)|杰佛逊县]]的[[阿瑟港_(德克萨斯州)|阿瑟港]]、[[尼德兰_(德克萨斯州)|尼德兰]]（{{lang|en|Nederland}}）、[[内奇斯港_(德克萨斯州)|内奇斯港]]（{{lang|en|Port Neches}}）、[[格罗夫斯_(德克萨斯州)|格罗夫斯]]（{{lang|en|Groves}}）和[[橙县_(得克萨斯州)|橙县]]的[[大桥城_(德克萨斯州)|大桥城]]（{{lang|en|Bridge City}}）上空。这也是2005年9月24日的[[飓风丽塔|飓风丽塔]]过后上述城市首度直接遭遇飓风袭击，前后相隔尚不足两年。登陆八小时后，温贝托已降级成热带风暴并进入[[路易斯安那州|路易斯安那州]]西南部。<ref name="disc6">{{cite report |author=James Franklin |date=2007-09-13 |title=Tropical Storm Humberto Discussion Six |publisher=National Hurricane Center |accessdate=2016-07-28 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160401151317/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2007/al09/al092007.discus.006.shtml |url=http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2007/al09/al092007.discus.006.shtml? |archivedate=2016-04-01 }}</ref>受上层[[风切变|风切变]]影响，风暴在陆地上空迅速减弱，于9月13日晚弱化成热带低气压。美国国家飓风中心在针对气旋发布的最后一份公告中指出，温贝托的残留有可能转向南下进入墨西哥湾。<ref name="disc7">{{cite report | author = Jack Beven | date = 2007-09-13 | title = Tropical Depression Humberto Discussion Seven | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2016-07-28 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2007/al09/al092007.discus.007.shtml? | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304214800/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2007/al09/al092007.discus.007.shtml | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2016-03-04 }}</ref>但气旋实际上继续向东北方向穿越[[美国东南部|美国东南部]]，于9月14日开始在[[乔治亚州|乔治亚州]]西北部上空逐渐消散，此后不久便退化成残留[[低气压|低气压区]]<ref name="hpc11">{{cite report | author = Christopher Hedge | date = 2007-09-14 | title = Public Advisory 11 for the Remnants of Humberto | publisher = Hydrometeorological Prediction Center | deadurl = yes | accessdate = 2008-01-106 | url = http://www.wpc.ncep.noaa.gov/tropical/HUMBERTO/HUMBERTO_11.html | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20080116182918/http://www.hpc.ncep.noaa.gov/tropical/HUMBERTO/HUMBERTO_11.html | archivedate = 2008-01-16 }}</ref>。

== 防灾措施 ==
[[File:Humbertoradar913.png|thumb]]

系统成为热带气旋后，德克萨斯州[[卡尔霍恩县_(得克萨斯州)|卡尔霍恩县]]的[[奥康纳港_(德克萨斯州)|奥康纳港]]（{{lang|en|Port O'Connor}}）到路易斯安那州[[卡梅伦_(路易斯安那州)|卡梅伦]]收到[[热带气旋警告|热带风暴警告]]，卡梅伦到[[弗米利恩堂区_(路易斯安那州)|弗米利恩堂区]]的[[因特拉科斯特尔城|因特拉科斯特尔城]]（{{lang|en|Intracoastal City}}）则接获热带风暴观察预警<ref name="pa1">{{cite report | author = James Franklin | date = 2007-09-12 | title = Tropical Depression Nine Public Advisory One | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2016-07-28 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160701071353/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2007/al09/al092007.public.001.shtml | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2007/al09/al092007.public.001.shtml? | archivedate = 2016-07-01 }}</ref>，并在气旋成为热带风暴后升级成热带风暴警告<ref name="pa2">{{cite report | author = James Franklin | date = 2007-09-12 | title = Tropical Storm Humberto Public Advisory Two | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2016-07-28 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160701070301/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2007/al09/al092007.public.002.shtml | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2007/al09/al092007.public.002.shtml? | archivedate = 2016-07-01 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。美国国家飓风中心在把温贝托升级成飓风后向德克萨斯州高岛至路易斯安那州卡梅伦发布飓风警告<ref name="pa4">{{cite report | author1 = Michelle Mainellimcinerney | author2 = Lixion Avila | date = 2007-09-13 | title = Hurricane Humberto Public Advisory Four | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2016-07-28 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160701072005/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2007/al09/al092007.public.004.shtml | deadurl = no | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2007/al09/al092007.public.004.shtml? | archivedate = 2016-07-01 }}</ref>。路易斯安那州西南部有[[路易斯安那州行政区划|多个堂区]]进入内陆热带风暴警告生效状态<ref name="hurloc">{{cite web |author=Roger Erickson |date=2007-09-13 |title=Hurricane Humberto Local Area Statement |publisher=Lake Charles National Weather Service |accessdate=2007-09-13 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5RpIxcj3U?url=http://www.srh.noaa.gov/wwamap/wwatxtget.php?cwa=lch |url=http://www.srh.noaa.gov/wwamap/wwatxtget.php?cwa=lch&wwa=hurricane%20local%20statement |deadurl=yes |archivedate=2007-09-13 }}</ref>，[[美国国家气象局|美国国家气象局]]风暴预测中心还向该州西南部多个沿海堂区发布龙卷风观察预警<ref name="disc6" />。[[卡尔克苏堂区_(路易斯安那州)|卡尔克苏堂区]]官员在风暴登陆前建议生活在低洼地区及洪水易发地区的居民考虑转移到更加安全的地点。[[莱克查尔斯_(路易斯安那州)|莱克查尔斯]]开有一间避难所，<ref name="hurloc" />风暴期间有29人前来躲避<ref name="lchpsh">{{cite web | author1 = Landreneau | author2 = Shamburger | author3 = Erickson | author4 = Rua | year = 2007 | title = Hurricane Humberto Post-Tropical Cyclone Report | publisher = Lake Charles, Louisiana National Weather Service | accessdate = 2016-07-28 | archivedate = 2016-07-28 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160728150006/http://www.srh.noaa.gov/hgx/?n=psh_humberto07_lch | deadurl = no | url = http://www.srh.noaa.gov/hgx/?n=psh_humberto07_lch }}</ref>。[[密西西比州|密西西比州]]和路易斯安那州部分地区在气旋途经期间进入洪水观察预警或警告生效状态<ref name="hpc9">{{cite web | author = Daniel Petersen | date = 2007-09-14 | title = Tropical Depression HUMBERTO Advisory Number 9 | publisher = Hydrometeorological Prediction Center | accessdate = 2016-07-28 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160728144714/http://www.wpc.ncep.noaa.gov/tropical/tropical_advisories.php?storm=HUMBERTO&adnum=9&dt=2007091409&status=td | archivedate = 2016-07-28 | deadurl = no | url = http://www.wpc.ncep.noaa.gov/tropical/tropical_advisories.php?storm=HUMBERTO&adnum=9&dt=2007091409&status=td }}</ref>。[[德克萨斯州州长|德克萨斯州州长]][[里克·佩里|里克·佩里]]为可能受灾的地区调动州内资源，部署200名[[德克萨斯武装部队|德克萨斯武装部队]]军人、六架[[UH-60黑鹰直升机|黑鹰直升机]]和两个水上救援组执行搜救任务。德克萨斯州指挥中心在气旋发展成型后不久开始运作。<ref name="texprep">{{cite web | author = Office of the Governor of Texas | year = 2007 | title = Texas Governor Perry Declares Three Texas Counties Disaster Areas | accessdate = 2012-02-23 | archivedate = 2012-02-23 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120223065349/http://www.allamericanpatriots.com/48732177_texas_texas_governor_perry_declares_three_texas_counties_disaster_areas | deadurl = yes | url = http://www.allamericanpatriots.com/48732177_texas_texas_governor_perry_declares_three_texas_counties_disaster_areas }}</ref>
