== 影响 ==

=== 德克萨斯州 ===
[[File:Hurricane_Humberto_2007_tree_damage.jpg|thumb]]

成型数小时前，低气压的外围雨带就开始进入德克萨斯州部分沿海地区上空<ref name="912two" />。随后几天，雨带从沿海地区经过，强烈的雷暴产生暴雨并引发轻度洪灾<ref name="houpsh">{{cite report | author1 = Blood | author2 = Overpeck | author3 = Lichter | year = 2007 | title = Hurricane Humberto Post-Tropical Cyclone Report | publisher = Houston, Texas National Weather Service | accessdate = 2016-07-28 | url = http://www.srh.noaa.gov/hgx/?n=psh_humberto07_hgx | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160728152016/http://www.srh.noaa.gov/hgx/?n=psh_humberto07_hgx | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2016-07-28 | date =  }}</ref>，全州以东湾河口（{{lang|en|East Bay Bayou}}）降水最多，达358.9毫米，也是温贝托产生雨量最多的所在<ref name="hpc11" />。[[海岸州立公园|海岸州立公园]]测得的持续风速最高，达到每小时112公里，阵风时速则有137公里。[[美国国家气象局|美国国家气象局]]估计[[杰佛逊县_(得克萨斯州)|杰佛逊县]]西南部和[[钱伯斯县_(得克萨斯州)|钱伯斯县]]最东南角的阵风时速超过145公里<ref name="nwswinds">{{cite web | author = National Weather Service | year = 2007 | title = Hurricane Humberto Winds & Lowest Pressures | accessdate = 2008-09-05 | archivedate = 2008-09-05 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20080905232052/http://www.srh.weather.gov/lch/tropical/humbertowinds.php | deadurl = yes | url = http://www.srh.weather.gov/lch/tropical/humbertowinds.php }}</ref>。另有船运航道测得185公里的阵风时速，但该数据未获正式认可<ref name="humbertotcr" />。风暴登陆期间产生轻度[[风暴潮|风暴潮]]，并以[[罗洛夫水道|罗洛夫水道]]（{{lang|en|Rollover Pass}}）最高，达到0.87米，风暴潮和海浪共同影响，导致轻度[[海滩侵蚀|海滩侵蚀]]<ref name="houpsh" />。

[[加尔维斯顿县|加尔维斯顿县]]有十户民宅被飓风彻底摧毁，另有19套受到严重破坏，多户民房的屋顶受损，许多道路封闭，导致全县约5000套房屋同外界的交通中断。由于土地含水量饱和，风暴沿途又产生狂风，许多树木被连根拔起，多条输电线缆中断，<ref name="houpsh" />至少有50根高压电线杆倒塌或严重受损，橙县和杰佛逊县有超过12万用户失去供电<ref name="lchpsh" />，[[安特吉公司|安特吉公司]]在德克萨斯州的用户中就有11万8000户断电<ref name="entergy">{{cite news | author = Dan Wallach | date = 2007-09-17 | title = 11:00 a.m.: Entergy determining costs of Humberto | publisher = Beaumont Enterprise}}</ref>。杰佛逊县和橙县发生大面积洪灾，[[博蒙特_(德克萨斯州)|博蒙特]]至少有20户民居被淹。多条道路也被洪水淹没，大桥城一名男子因房子旁边的车棚坍塌致死。<ref name="lchpsh" />媒体报导起初声称气旋造成的破坏数额高达五亿美元<ref>{{cite news | agency = [[美联社|Associated Press]] | publisher = MSNBC | date = 2007-09-14 | accessdate = 2016-07-28 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160305042516/http://www.nbcnews.com/id/20771578/ | archivedate = 2016-03-05 | title = Power being restored in Texas, Louisiana | url = http://www.nbcnews.com/id/20771578/ | deadurl = no }}</ref>，但经最终估算大幅调低到5000万美元左右<ref name="humbertotcr" />。

温贝托还令[[石油|石油]]生产受阻，阿瑟港至少有四家炼油厂（分属[[瓦莱罗能源|瓦莱罗能源]]、[[艾克森美孚|艾克森美孚]]、[[道达尔|道达尔]]和[[莫蒂瓦企业公司|莫蒂瓦企业公司]]）因停电而不得不停产。受此影响，9月12日盘中油价升破每桶80美元，次日收盘时还以每桶80.09美元创下历史新高。<ref>{{cite news | first = Matthew | last = Robinson | title = Oil hits record over $80 | date = 2007-09-13 | publisher = [[路透社|Reuters]]}}</ref><ref name="saefong">{{cite news | archivedate = 2012-02-15 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120215104540/http://markets.usatoday.com/custom/usatoday-com/html-story.asp?markets=COMMODITIES&guid=%7B345BD322-D12B-478C-B0D7-FBFE17BC8866%7D | last = Saefong | first = Myra P. | url = http://markets.usatoday.com/custom/usatoday-com/html-story.asp?markets=COMMODITIES&guid=%7B345BD322%2DD12B%2D478C%2DB0D7%2DFBFE17BC8866%7D | title = Oil futures mark first-ever close above $80 a barrel | publisher = [[今日美国|USA Today]] | date = 2007-09-13 | accessdate = 2012-02-15 | deadurl = yes }}</ref>天然气期货价格在风暴来袭前上涨八个百分点，但次日就基本跌回原价<ref name="saefong" />。

据[[联邦紧急事务管理局|联邦紧急事务管理局]]统计，德克萨斯州共有1464户居民受到飓风影响，其中有25套民房被毁，96套遭受重创，另有240套受到轻度破坏。对灾民提供的个别援助总计耗资477万6334美元，垃圾清理及其它公共援助成本共有668万2074美元。各地[[人均收入|人均收入]]以杰佛逊县降幅最大，有22.38美元。<ref>{{cite web | publisher = Federal Emergency Management Agency | date = 2007-10-16 | accessdate = 2016-07-28 | title = Texas Hurricane Humberto – Denial | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303202432/http://www.fema.gov/pdf/news/pda/101608_tx_denial.pdf | deadurl = no | url = http://www.fema.gov/pdf/news/pda/101608_tx_denial.pdf | format = PDF | archivedate = 2016-03-03 }}</ref>

=== 路易斯安那州 ===
[[File:Humberto_2007_rainfall.gif|thumb]]

温贝托进入路易斯安那州时仍有热带风暴强度，但也在逐渐减弱，该州西南部普降小到中雨。全州正式纪录中的最高阵风时速为69公里，不过也有非正式数据表明[[温顿_(路易斯安那州)|温顿]]的阵风时速达到89公里。<ref name="nwswinds" />风暴沿途降下暴雨，降雨量最高的[[德里德_(路易斯安那州)|德里德]]有210毫米之多<ref name="HPCGCrain">{{cite web | author = David M. Roth | publisher = Hydrometeorological Prediction Center | year = 2008 | accessdate = 2016-07-28 | title = Tropical Cyclone Rainfall for the Gulf Coast | archivedate = 2016-03-04 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304092617/http://www.wpc.ncep.noaa.gov/tropical/rain/tcgulfcoast.html | deadurl = no | url = http://www.wpc.ncep.noaa.gov/tropical/rain/tcgulfcoast.html }}</ref>。降水导致[[弗米利恩河_(路易斯安那州)|弗米利恩河]]（{{lang|en|Vermilion River}}）位于[[拉法叶_(路易斯安那州)|拉法叶]]境内部分河段泛滥，但程度尚轻。路易斯安那州沿海地区的风暴潮不强，最高的赛普里蒙特角（{{lang|en|Cypremont Point}}）也只有0.65米<ref name="humbertotcr" />，没有报导表明这些风暴潮曾引发海滩侵蚀<ref name="lchpsh" />。

[[波尔格堂区_(路易斯安那州)|波尔格堂区]]发生大面积洪灾，德里德有许多民宅被淹。该州西南部有多条道路因洪水封闭，其中包括[[171号美国国道|171号美国国道]]和多条州级公路。局部地区受到大风破坏，特别是路易斯安那州和德克萨斯州边界附近，部分树木倒塌，供电线缆中断。路易斯安那州西南部共有约1万3000用户失去供电。<ref name="lchpsh" />[[弗米利恩堂区_(路易斯安那州)|弗米利恩堂区]]有一场[[藤田级数|藤田级数]]达到{{lang|en|F}}1的[[龙卷风|龙卷风]]短暂着陆，刮掉一户民房的屋顶，还刮倒多棵树木，致使多条电缆中断。整个路易斯安那州的损失总额估计为52万5000美元。<ref name="NCDC">{{cite journal | author = National Climatic Data Center | date = 2007-09 | volume = 49 | number = 9 | accessdate = 2016-07-29 | title = Storm Data and Unusual Weather Phenomena with Late Reports and Corrections | issn = 0039-1972 | editor1 = William Angel | editor2 = Stuart Hinson | editor3 = Rhonda Herndon | url = http://www1.ncdc.noaa.gov/pub/orders/IPS/IPS-35981BBA-E467-46F2-8DB5-BBD789BB1AC1.pdf | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160729032440/http://www1.ncdc.noaa.gov/pub/orders/IPS/IPS-35981BBA-E467-46F2-8DB5-BBD789BB1AC1.pdf | archivedate = 2016-07-29 | deadurl = yes | format = PDF | publisher = [[美国国家海洋和大气管理局|National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration]] | location = Asheville, NC }}[http://www.ncdc.noaa.gov/IPS/sd/sd.html 此网站] {{Wayback|url=http://www.ncdc.noaa.gov/IPS/sd/sd.html |date=20160414065723 }}可查询1959年至今每个月美国的异常天气影响信息，每个月都有单独的平面出版物，这里可以返回PDF格式在线查看，有效期24小时，请选择2007-09获得所需信息</ref>

=== 美国东南部 ===
气旋环流消散后的残留在美国东南部多个州产生中等程度雨量，还在[[南卡罗莱纳州|南卡罗莱纳州]]和[[北卡罗莱纳州|北卡罗莱纳州]]催生出多场龙卷风，部分地区因此遭受大面积破坏<ref>{{cite web | author = Raleigh, North Carolina National Weather Service | date = 2007-09-14 | title = Hurricane Humberto Special Weather Statement | accessdate = 2011-06-11 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20110611170134/http://www.erh.noaa.gov/rah/news/content/RDUPNSRAH.20070914.html | url = http://www.erh.noaa.gov/rah/news/content/RDUPNSRAH.20070914.html | archivedate = 2011-06-11 }}</ref>。密西西比州部分低洼地区因暴雨引发洪灾。[[海恩兹县_(密西西比州)|海恩兹县]]有座小型铁路桥被冲毁，搭乘[[美铁|美铁]]的乘客不得不另乘汽车赶赴目的地。一人因车开入洪水泛滥的街道而受伤。[[阿拉巴马州|阿拉巴马州]]的降雨量达到129毫米，虽令低洼地区轻度积水，但也有助于暂时缓解旱情。乔治亚州北部局部地区因暴雨出现山洪爆发，导致多条道路封闭。气旋残留产生强烈的雷阵雨，还引发时速82公里的阵风和直径约两厘米的[[冰雹|冰雹]]。北卡罗莱纳州各地经确认共出现十场{{lang|en|F}}0级龙卷风，<ref name="NCDC"/>对多户民宅构成轻度破坏，但没有造成人员伤亡<ref>{{cite web | author = WRAL5.com | date = 2007-09-14 | title = Humberto's Ghost Lashes Triangle With Winds and Rain | accessdate = 2016-07-29 | url = http://www.wral.com/news/local/story/1817052/ | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303190214/http://www.wral.com/news/local/story/1817052/ | archivedate = 2016-03-03 }}</ref>。风暴残留产生的暴雨还在部分道路沿线引发山洪，导致路段封闭。南卡罗莱纳州[[劳伦斯县_(南卡罗莱纳州)|劳伦斯县]]有一场{{lang|en|F}}1级龙卷风着陆，对多户民房构成中等程度破坏后升空。<ref name="NCDC" />

== 善后 ==
[[File:Residents_at_stations_after_Hurricane_Humberto_2007.jpg|thumb]]

温贝托登陆数小时后，里克·佩里宣布加尔维斯顿县、杰佛逊县和橙县为灾区，以便灾民获得州内救助资源<ref name="texprep" />。州长还于9月21日请求总统宣告相应地区为联邦灾区<ref>{{cite news | author = Sarah More | year = 2007 | title = Much-watched storm remains nameless as it drifts onto land | publisher = Beaumont Enterprise}}</ref>。[[联邦紧急事务管理局|联邦紧急事务管理局]]派出四个工作组前往受灾最重的三个县评估飓风破坏程度<ref>{{cite news | author = Harvey Rice | title = Gov. Perry may request federal aid for Humberto victims: Teams expected to complete survey today or Thursday . | publisher = Houston Chronicle | accessdate = 2016-07-29 | date = 2007-09-19 | archivedate = 2016-07-29 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160729092933/http://www.chron.com/news/houston-texas/article/Gov-Perry-may-request-federal-aid-for-Humberto-1537645.php | deadurl = no | url = http://www.chron.com/news/houston-texas/article/Gov-Perry-may-request-federal-aid-for-Humberto-1537645.php }}</ref>。经过评估，工作组认为温贝托造成破坏的严重程度还不足以申请联邦援助，联邦紧急事务管理局因此拒绝州长佩里的请求<ref>{{cite news | author = Christine Rappleye | publisher = ''The Enterprise'' | date = 2007-10-20 | accessdate = 2016-07-29 | title = FEMA: Humberto was not a disaster | url = http://nl.newsbank.com/nl-search/we/Archives?p_product=BT&p_theme=bt&p_action=search&p_maxdocs=200&p_topdoc=1&p_text_direct-0=11C783D8588BEB98&p_field_direct-0=document_id&p_perpage=10&p_sort=YMD_date:D&s_trackval=GooglePM | archive-date = 2020-09-08 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200908152741/http://nl.newsbank.com/nl-search/we/Archives?p_product=BT&p_theme=bt&p_action=search&p_maxdocs=200&p_topdoc=1&p_text_direct-0=11C783D8588BEB98&p_field_direct-0=document_id&p_perpage=10&p_sort=YMD_date%3AD&s_trackval=GooglePM | dead-url = no }}</ref>。估计[[玻利瓦尔半岛|玻利瓦尔半岛]]（{{lang|en|Bolivar Peninsula}}）在风暴过后共有1147立方米瓦砾和2293立方米树枝需要清理<ref>{{cite news | agency = [[美联社|Associated Press]] | publisher = USA Today | date = 2007-09-15 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121102080822/http://usatoday30.usatoday.com/weather/storms/hurricanes/2007-09-15-hurricane-humberto_N.htm | deadurl = no | accessdate = 2016-07-29 | title = Cleanup begins after Hurricane Humberto | url = http://usatoday30.usatoday.com/weather/storms/hurricanes/2007-09-15-hurricane-humberto_N.htm | archivedate = 2012-11-02 }}</ref>。

